## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of data up to October 2023 and may not reflect the most recent developments in marijuana legalization. Additionally, the analysis is based on secondary sources, which may contain biases or incomplete information. Further research, including primary data collection and analysis, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the topic.